NAME

      gcloud sql instances promote-replica - promotes Cloud SQL read replica to
         a stand-alone instance

SYNOPSIS

      gcloud sql instances promote-replica REPLICA [--async] [GLOBAL-FLAG ...]

DESCRIPTION

      Promotes Cloud SQL read replica to a stand-alone instance.

POSITIONAL ARGUMENTS

      REPLICA

         Cloud SQL read replica ID.

FLAGS

      --async

         Do not wait for the operation to complete.

GLOBAL FLAGS

      Run $ gcloud help for a description of flags available to all commands.

NOTES

      This command is in the Google Cloud SDK sql component. See installing
      components if it is not installed.

